PortSystem 1.0

name		tcptraceroute
version		1.5beta4
categories	net
platforms	darwin
maintainers	mww@opendarwin.org
description	a traceroute implementation using TCP packets
long_description	${description}

homepage	http://michael.toren.net/code/tcptraceroute/
